3\mid f(n) \iff  4\mid n
n+1
g(n)=f(n)\bmod 3
g(0)=0
g(1)=1
g(n+1)=\big(g(n)+g(n-1)\big)\bmod 3
n>0
g(2)=1
g(3)=2
g(4)=(1+2)\bmod 3=0
g(5)=2
3\mid f(n)
